Installation Instructions for the VoteCollector Plugin
======================================================


1. Install OpenSlides

    See instructions at http://openslides.org/

2. Install the VoteCollector


3. Install the Plugin

    a) Move the directory 'votecollector' into the 'openslides' directory.

    b) Edit file 'openslides/settigs.py':
       Add 'votecollector' to 'INSTALLED_PLUGINS'. For example:

       INSTALLED_PLUGINS = (
           'votecollector',
       )

    c) If you already have the database file (database.db) in your OpenSlides
       root directory, run:

       python manage.py syncdb

       If you do not have the database file, run:

       python start.py

4. Run OpenSlides

    python start.py

    If you get a new tab 'VoteCollector', your installation was successfull.
